{"type": "article", "id": 18592, "title": "六边形地砖", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-07T07:52:44Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 51, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135339Bpcd7vW0CValhEyn.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是瓷砖设计工作室 DSIGNIO 为西班牙瓷砖品牌 Harmony-Peronda 设计的六边形地砖，让地板变得像一个迷宫。每一块瓷砖都是白色的背景，上面用彩色画了一根竖线和两个弧，都在每条边的中点与其他瓷砖相接。可能构成闭合的圆，也可能是各种弯曲角度的曲线，在随意搭配中让地板变得有活力。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135336AKCfZXzS0hVtdIPp.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.42857143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135337ib9mhQWFUZvlJ25L.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.42833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135337WzlwGVXDRsQCLcAO.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.42833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135338swQXA2ofSUmr6b3j.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.42833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}